---
import { CountUp } from "../ui/animations/count-up";
import { Highlight } from "../ui/animations/highlight";
import { Typewriter } from "../ui/animations/typewriter";
import { Underline } from "../ui/animations/underline";

const data = [
  {
    title: "BRANDS LAUNCHED",
    value: 13,
    description: "6 BRANDS ACROSS 3 INDUSTRIES",
  },
];
---

<section class="space-y-4 mb-16">
  <div
    class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 group/underline max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4"
  >
    <h2 class="text-title-lg font-bold text-center font-sans relative">
      <Underline bottom="8px" height="6px"> SCOREBOARD </Underline>
    </h2>
    <svg
      width="114"
      height="110"
      viewBox="0 0 114 110"
      fill="none"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      class="size-title-lg"
    >
      <path
        d="M8 10.8896H103.71V102.81"
        stroke="black"
        stroke-width="20"
        stroke-miterlimit="10"></path>
      <path
        d="M8 102.81L101.82 9"
        stroke="black"
        stroke-width="20"
        stroke-miterlimit="10"></path>
    </svg>
  </div>
  <div class="relative">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-background-secondary -z-20 overflow-hidden">
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[3fr_2fr] py-8">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-center gap-4">
        <div
          class="text-[5rem]/[0.9] sm:text-[7rem]/[0.9] md:text-[10rem]/[0.9] lg:text-[12rem]/[0.9] text-end font-sans font-bold"
        >
          <CountUp client:load value={13} />
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2 mb-2 px-4">
          <div
            class="text-2xl/[0.9] sm:text-3xl/[0.9] lg:text-5xl/[0.9] font-sans font-bold"
          >
            <Highlight client:load>BRANDS</Highlight>
            <br /> LAUNCHED
          </div>
          <div class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-2xl/[1] text-light">
            <Typewriter
              client:load
              delay={10}
              text="6 BRANDS ACROSS \n 3 INDUSTRIES"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <img
        src="/assets/right-1.png"
        alt="Scoreboard"
        class="object-contain scale-90 sm:scale-100 md:scale-120 origin-right h-36 sm:h-48 md:h-80 justify-self-end"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[2fr_3fr] py-8">
      <div class="order-1 md:order-2 flex items-start justify-center gap-4">
        <div
          class="text-[5rem]/[0.9] sm:text-[7rem]/[0.9] md:text-[10rem]/[0.9] lg:text-[12rem]/[0.9] text-end font-sans font-bold"
        >
          +<CountUp client:load value={260} />
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2 mb-2 px-4">
          <div
            class="text-2xl/[0.9] sm:text-3xl/[0.9] lg:text-5xl/[0.9] font-sans font-bold"
          >
            <Highlight client:load>Members</Highlight>
          </div>
          <div class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-2xl/[1] max-w-64 text-light">
            <Typewriter
              client:load
              delay={10}
              text="EXPERTS ACROSS LOGISTICS, STRATEGY, R&D, MARKETING, AND OPERATIONS."
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <img
        src="/assets/left-1.png"
        alt="Scoreboard"
        class="order-2 md:order-1 object-contain scale-95 sm:scale-110 md:scale-300 origin-left md:-translate-y-32 h-64 sm:h-72 md:h-80 justify-self-start"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[3fr_2fr] py-8">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-center gap-1">
        <div
          class="text-[5rem]/[0.9] sm:text-[7rem]/[0.9] md:text-[10rem]/[0.9] lg:text-[12rem]/[0.9] text-end font-sans font-bold"
        >
          +<CountUp client:load value={89} />
        </div>
        <div
          class="text-3xl/[0.9] md:text-4xl/[0.9] lg:text-6xl/[0.9] tracking-tighter font-sans font-bold"
        >
          M$
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2 mb-2 px-4">
          <div
            class="text-2xl/[0.9] sm:text-3xl/[0.9] lg:text-5xl/[0.9] font-sans font-bold"
          >
            ANNUAL <br /><Highlight client:load> REVENUE</Highlight>
          </div>
          <div class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-2xl/[1] max-w-52 text-light">
            <Typewriter client:load delay={10} text="OVER THE LAST 3 YEARS" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <img
        src="/assets/right-2.png"
        alt="Scoreboard"
        class="object-contain scale-95 sm:scale-110 md:scale-150 origin-right h-48 sm:h-56 md:h-80 justify-self-end"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[2fr_3fr] py-8">
      <div class="order-1 md:order-2 flex items-start justify-center gap-4">
        <div
          class="text-[5rem]/[0.9] sm:text-[7rem]/[0.9] md:text-[10rem]/[0.9] lg:text-[12rem]/[0.9] text-end font-sans font-bold"
        >
          <CountUp client:load value={11} />
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2 mb-2 px-4">
          <div
            class="text-2xl/[0.9] sm:text-3xl/[0.9] lg:text-5xl/[0.9] font-sans font-bold"
          >
            <Highlight client:load>OPERATIONAL</Highlight><br /> SITES
          </div>
          <div class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-2xl/[1] max-w-64 text-light">
            <Typewriter
              client:load
              delay={10}
              text="INCLUDING LOGISTICS HUBS, PRODUCTION UNITS & HQ."
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <img
        src="/assets/left-2.png"
        alt="Scoreboard"
        class="order-2 md:order-1 object-contain scale-95 sm:scale-110 md:scale-200 origin-left h-48 sm:h-56 md:h-80 justify-self-start"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[3fr_2fr] py-8">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-center">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-end">
          <div
            class="text-[5rem]/[0.9] sm:text-[7rem]/[0.9] md:text-[10rem]/[0.9] lg:text-[12rem]/[0.9] text-end font-sans font-bold"
          >
            +<CountUp client:load value={6530} />
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-2 mb-2 px-4">
            <div
              class="text-2xl/[0.9] sm:text-3xl/[0.9] lg:text-5xl/[0.9] font-sans font-bold"
            >
              Active B2B <br /><Highlight client:load>PARTNERS</Highlight>
            </div>
            <div
              class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-2xl/[1] max-w-52 text-light"
            >
              <Typewriter
                client:load
                delay={10}
                text="PHARMACIES, \nDISTRIBUTORS \n& RETAILERS."
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <img
        src="/assets/right-3.png"
        alt="Scoreboard"
        class="object-contain scale-95 sm:scale-110 md:scale-150 origin-right h-48 sm:h-56 md:h-80 justify-self-end"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[2fr_3fr] items-end py-8">
      <img
        src="/assets/left-3.png"
        alt="Scoreboard"
        class="order-2 md:order-1 object-contain origin-left h-56 sm:h-72 md:h-[28rem] lg:h-[32rem] w-auto max-w-full justify-self-start self-end scale-100 sm:scale-110 md:scale-125"
      />
      <div
        class="order-1 md:order-2 flex items-center flex-col justify-center gap-4 mb-8"
      >
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div
            class="text-[12rem]/[0.9] lg:text-[15rem]/[0.9] text-end font-sans font-bold"
          >
            <CountUp client:load value={7} />
          </div>
          <div>
            <div
              class="text-[3rem]/[0.9] lg:text-[3.4rem]/[0.9] tracking-tighter font-sans font-bold"
            >
              PRODUCTS<br />
            </div>
            <div
              class="text-[2.5rem]/[0.9] lg:text-[2.9rem]/[0.9] tracking-tighter font-sans font-bold"
            >
              OR SERVICES <br />
            </div>
            <div
              class="text-[6rem]/[0.9] lg:text-[7rem]/[0.9] tracking-tighter font-sans font-bold"
            >
              <Highlight client:load>/ MIN</Highlight>
            </div>
            <div class="text-lg lg:text-xl/[1] [word-spacing:0.5em] text-light">
          <Typewriter
            client:load
            delay={80}
            split="word"
            text="EVERY MINUTE"
          />
        </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center space-y-10 pb-50">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-center gap-1">
        <div
          class="text-[5rem]/[0.9] sm:text-[7rem]/[0.9] md:text-[10rem]/[0.9] lg:text-[12rem]/[0.9] text-end font-sans font-bold"
        >
          +<CountUp client:load value={150} />
        </div>
        <div
          class="text-3xl/[0.9] md:text-4xl/[0.9] lg:text-6xl/[0.9] tracking-tighter font-sans font-bold"
        >
          M$
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2 mb-2 px-4">
          <div
            class="text-2xl/[0.9] sm:text-3xl/[0.9] lg:text-5xl/[0.9] font-sans font-bold"
          >
            TOTAL <br /><Highlight client:load> WORTH</Highlight>
          </div>
          <div class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-2xl/[1] max-w-52 text-light">
            <Typewriter client:load delay={10} text="OF THINKERCAREGROUP" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl max-w-2xl text-light text-center max-md:px-4"
      >
        BEHIND EVERY NUMBER LIES A STORY OF AMBITION TURNED INTO ACTION, IN JUST
        A FEW YEARS, WE DIDN’T SIMPLY ENTER THE CARE INDUSTRY WE REWROTE THE
        RULES <br /><br /> THESE FIGURES ARE NOT VANITY METRICS, THEY ARE THE PROOF
        THAT WHEN BOLD IDEAS MEET RELENTLESS EXECUTION, GROWTH BECOMES INEVITABLE
        THEY SHOW HOW FAST WE MOVE, HOW FAR WE’VE COME, AND HOW MUCH FURTHER WE’RE
        READY TO GO.
        <br /><br /> BECAUSE FOR US, NUMBERS AREN’T THE END GOAL, THEY’RE ONLY THE
        BEGINNING.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
